      "description": "<p>Aflição</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Fazendo movimentos manuais e entoando algumas palavras aflige um personagem alvo com a morbidez.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Esforço:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 4.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Tempo de preparo:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 1 ação.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Alcance:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 15/30m.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Dano:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 2 Biológico: Podre.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Efeitos:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> aplica MOD-6 a Saúde e dobra a Peste causada.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Duração:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 1 hora.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Pré-requisitos:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> <em>Pestilência</em> e Sabakismo N2.</span></p>",
